{"tid":2031672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：美國將退出《開放天空條約》","createTime":"2020-05-23T14:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T15:12:37.000Z","uid":75656,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dc717738d3c4280422fec10a23231d40a6b94194","tid":2031672,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:18:43.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國總統特朗普表示，由於俄羅斯沒有遵守《開放天空條約》，美方將會退出條約。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部亦批評俄羅斯公然和持續違反有關條約，對美國及美國的盟友夥伴造成軍事威脅，呼籲俄方恪守責任和承擔義務。<br />\n<br />\n北約成員國大使周五召開緊急會議商討應對，北約大部分成員國都促請美國不要退出條約。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯外交部否認違反條約，又指美國退出會影響所有條約簽署國的利益。<br />\n<br />\n美國和前蘇聯以及其他三十多個國家92年簽訂《開放天空條約》，允許簽約國之間的飛機飛越各國領空，進行非武裝空中偵察，監察各國控制軍備情況。條約在2002年正式生效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=391852\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391852&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=6a9f4543\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391852&h=7660a9ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=391852</a>"},{"pid":"05b9d3b5e96d23039d484dd0223851258200c0c9","tid":2031672,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:21:14.000Z","msg":"抹黑宇宙未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e99e380d932ad602e33b4d9ee5a51ec7f40bcc","tid":2031672,"uid":348453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1492b6339ac4dde83004078f5f93568beaa75353","tid":2031672,"uid":215876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:21:59.000Z","msg":"天空不再開放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897c2d96f6430ae3b69f85eb170a79837453ce99","tid":2031672,"uid":283700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:22:17.000